Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rendezvous without using your smartphones!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, FUJIWARA's Fujimoto was the guest.\NWhat’s the first theme?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“Historical buildings.”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very wide range.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you have some options?\N- I came up with two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- I used to go to the driving range at Gaien a lot.\N- Picture Gallery?\N- Yeah, that’s old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the National Diet Building, isn't it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the way it feels.\NYou still think this is awesome, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Nippon Budoukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They struggled a lot with this theme.\NSo no one could meet someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The next theme was furniture stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How about IKEA?\NWhere is IKEA?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is still Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:00:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we get Tanaka out of the regular members?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of them met in front of Otsuka Furniture in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is where they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, Hosei, and Endo are in Shinjuku.\NHamada is in Shibuya.\NFujimoto is in Nakameguro.\NAnd Tanaka is in Harajuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Will all six be able to meet tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Subbed by RAIDEN1017]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The next theme will be announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,“Kushikatsu Tanaka”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to various restaurants on Gaki before, but sorry, I've forgotten everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:02:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They used to come to each of Kushikatsu Tanaka's restaurants for the "Kushikatsu Tanaka Marathon" segment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 4 years ago that they went to each restaurant in the 23 wards of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We went there on Gaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's memory is hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, what about Fujimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have walked through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one restaurant I know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where is it?\N- *****.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Along Setagaya Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to the restaurant along Setagaya Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about Hamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a lot of restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know that restaurant in *****.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one near that intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He remembered the restaurant from memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish at least Fujimon and Tanaka would come there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make it a 3-on-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-You were told by them about the number of people.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo said that in a smug.\NSo I said, "Don't be so cocky!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- He said that in a smug?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "If there are three of us here, then we are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said, “Hey bitch!!”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, what about three guys who can talk to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one near Tokyo Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- How do you know that?\N- There was a wide five-way near there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They decided to go to the restaurant near the Tokyo Tower that Matsumoto remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you have any ideas now?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In Setagaya area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But what street was that?\NKomazawa Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there is one in Shin-Yokohama station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is no way they would come there.\NEven I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka was deciding between the Setagaya and the Shin-Yokohama Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He should head for the Setagaya considering the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are 10 Kushikatsu Tanaka restaurants in Setagaya Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Tanaka's answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please head to ****.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As I remember, that is on Komazawa Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as Tanaka remembers, there is the restaurant on the Komazawa Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I really need to meet with someone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I want to meet someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Tanaka's prayers be answered?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is where the six of them are heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a difficult theme because of the number of restaurants.\NWhat will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto was heading for Setagaya via the Old Yamanote Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be in front of the station or some other convenient location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that just down the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A restaurant you found by chance is a no good by the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that a no good?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, It was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!\NYes, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this no good?\NIt's not no good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't come up with this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I said, "It could have been down the street."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- I should have gone to there!\N- This is another place where celebrities might pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A few minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is it serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurant isn't open yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The restaurant in Shinsen-cho Fujimoto passed was the one Hamada had chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They regrettably missed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking about that restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please say, "Go to that restaurant.”\N- But, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that too strict?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Fujimoto had chosen Kushikatsu Tanaka in Shinsen-cho, he could have met Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Which restaurant did he arrive at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think you arrived quite early.\N- Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kushikatsu Tanaka in Setagaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He waited for the others with slight expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, Tanaka arrived near his destination restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I arrived at the restaurant in *****.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Would he be able to meet someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\NTanaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm so happy!\N- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka came to “Tanaka”.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The street Tanaka thought was the Komazawa Street was the Setagaya Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He met Fujimoto with flying colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And time was up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the restaurant where Matsumoto's team arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They confirmed each other's whereabouts over the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you guys meet someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka and Fujimon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We are in Setagaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about that restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed you caught a stray dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A stray dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, as long as we catch that stray dog, we'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Hamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at a restaurant near the intersection of Shinsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that the Old Yamanote Street?\N- Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the road from Daikanyama to Ebisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And where are the three guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We are in front of a pizza shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They were heading to a restaurant near Tokyo Tower, relying on Matsumoto's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kushikatsu...huh?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Frozen pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Frozen pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That closed on November 23, 2020.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:10:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This restaurant, which used to be Kushikatsu Tanaka, has become a frozen pizza production and sales store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently the restaurant I remembered is now a pizza shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It had turned into a pizza shop, that's a problem!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This restaurant turned two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's no good.\N- If it's changed into a different restaurant two years ago, it's not gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But the skewers are still on the ground in front of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys think it's okay even if there's no restaurant!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're meeting next!\NSee you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, the phone went dead.\N- They hung up the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I complained and they hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They should give me more praise for catching Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like that way of talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hours have passed since the start!\NHere is where the six of them are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:11:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They are relatively far apart, so it's important to take someone's thoughts into account when deciding where to meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Next theme announced!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It says something strange again.\N[Large Bookstore]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be that place.\NThere is no other place but that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,1, 2, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinokuniya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did only I say it?\NThe person who said Shinjuku was also silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is Kinokuniya the big bookstore in Shinjuku?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that store in Daikanyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tsutaya?\N- Oh, Is that Tsutaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, which one's better?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you even thinking about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They headed for the Kinokuniya bookstore in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, something unexpected happened to Fujimoto and Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A large bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean we say where we are going at the same time and match?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where it will be, but I'll definitely meet you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's show them our bachelor potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- We move together.\N- Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this segment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, this is a very popular segment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto spoke this way at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You said something about us split up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're not watching Gaki, are you?\N- I'm watching it! This is a very popular segment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't understand this at all.\NOuch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "Let's meet again!”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand what you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto didn't understand the rules at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,“Let's meet again!!”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do you have to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He was teased by Tanaka constantly.\NFor the time being, they discussed in the taxi which large bookstore they would go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hamada-san is in Shibuya.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right now?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But there aren't any large bookstores in Shibuya, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What came to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I just came up with is Sanseido in Carrot Tower in Sangenjaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where did you come up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's next to Takashimaya in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it next to Studio Alta?\N- Next to Alta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, next to Takashimaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the Kinokuniya bookstore next to Alta in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- There is a Kinokuniya bookstore there.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The store Fujimoto is talking about is Kinokuniya's Foreign Book Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:14:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It is just a few minutes' walk from the main store.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Their fate depends on which one they choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please head for Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, it is in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They headed for Shinjuku for the time being, without giving an answer for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, what about this lone man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A large bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Two old stores come to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm here and I can't ignore *****.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was Hamada's answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I should probably go to *****.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they will go to Kinokuniya in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He decided that no one would come to the Kinokuniya bookstore that the other members had chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What will be Hamada's fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Four hours and five minutes had passed since the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the chance for Matsumoto, Hosei, and Endo to meet Fujimoto and Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada predicted that no one would come to the Kinokuniya in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto and Tanaka headed for Shinjuku, still wondering where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's consider Hamada-san's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have to consider Hamada-san.\NWasn't there a Junkudo bookstore somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- There is also a Kodomo-no-Shiro in Aoyama.\N- Yes, there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the answer they came up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- It is next to Alta, after all.\N- Yeah, that Kinokuniya bookstore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that is famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Their destination was decided to be the Shinjuku main store of Kinokuniya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And another team was going to Kinokuniya bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the store they arrived at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is the only place.\N- And it's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They chose the Kinokuniya Shinjuku main store, as did Fujimoto and Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Matsumoto had one concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am not sure if I would have come here if I were alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, where would you have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:17:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have gone to the Tsutaya bookstore in Daikanyama for my troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If no one came after all this waiting, it would be impossible this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto's hunch was right on target.\NHamada came to the Tsutaya bookstore in Daikanyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they all go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry, time is up.\N-Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm so shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Fujimoto and Tanaka really go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They confirmed each other's whereabouts over the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We waited so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited for the three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We met!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto and Tanaka were on their way to the Kinokuniya main store in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before Tanaka arrived at Shinjuku, he remembered the Tsutaya bookstore in Daikanyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Tsutaya in Daikanyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, please head there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutaya in Daikanyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Expecting Hamada to be there, the two of them hastily changed their destination and headed for Daikanyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty minutes after the change of destination, they arrived at the Tsutaya in Daikanyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They met Hamada with flying colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you guys so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you guys planning to come here all along?\NOr did you change here on the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We were heading for Kinokuniya in Shinjuku at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the way I remembered Tsutaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,FLAAAAASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you guys really go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We are in Kinokuniya in Shinjuku!\NThis place is venerable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tanaka.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you have gone if you were alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was headed for the store in the carrot tower in Sangenchaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nuts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like Sangenchaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like Carrot Tower, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to finish with next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish with next one
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Isn't he a bit annoying?\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because he met someone earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The next theme was announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it a very simple theme!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what’s the hell is this!?\N[Tree-lined street]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the only place for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A tree-lined street.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- It’s okay.\N- This is that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you come up with yours already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- I came up with it even before I saw the theme.\N- What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.\NI know.\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, Hosei, and Endo were at the Avenue of Gingko Trees in Meiji Jingu Gaien, one of the most popular sightseeing spots in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Hamada and the other three arrived near their destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The stupid team doesn't come at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The smart team has been waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The smart team is always waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- They are evil.\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stupid is evil.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You agree with me too much, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's a light coming from over there.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a light like ours coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, you guys are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I met you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other place but here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help this time, Fujimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught this stray dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel I was very helpful too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- But...\N- Hey, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- There is one thing that surprised me.\N- You don't have to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I met him at the Kushikatsu Tanaka in Setagaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so happy.\NThen we had a call with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The next theme was a large bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After he saw that theme,\Nhe said, “Okay, Tanaka, let's meet next again!”\NAnd he left!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He has never watched this show before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy thought that all six of us had to be there at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the rule, we'll never get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.97,0:23:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be more fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be more fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a report here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.48,0:23:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki-san called us the smart team and you guys the stupid team.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NReally thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.\NI just agreed with Matsumoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I only agreed with him because....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See, he's pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder Lamborghini is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lamborghini is also angry with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[subbed by RAIDEN1017]
